在鼎盛时期，阿尼拥有10-20万居民，地位相当于于同期的[[君士坦丁堡|君士坦丁堡]]、[[巴格达|巴格达]]和[[开罗|开罗]]。<ref name="SAE">{{hy icon}} Ghafadaryan, Karo. ''«Անի»'' (''Ani''). Soviet Armenian Encyclopedia. vol. i. Yerevan: Armenian SSR: Armenian Academy of Sciences, 1974, pp. 407–412.</ref> <!-- STRAY INFO: 50,000–100,000<ref>The Armenians,  Anne Elizabeth Redgate, page 210, 2000</ref> -->
